<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-23-0883 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper describes a new method to evaluate diagonal dominance in atransfer matrix for a unilateral decoupled system. Three basic decouplingmethods are discussed. The central systems designed with these methodshave been used in three units with once-through boilers and have goodcontrol qualities. Finally the ways to improve the availability of controlsystems are discussed.</TEXT></DOC>